description:
Japanese title: Kakashi Gaiden ~ Senjō no bōizuraifu ~ Kōhen (カカシ外伝～戦場のボーイズライフ～後編)

Obito ignores Kakashi’s order to continue with the mission and leaves to save Rin, who was kidnapped by the Rock ninja. But the enemies detect Obito’s arrival and defeat him. Kakashi arrives at the last minute and saves Obito…
name: Kakashi Chronicles ~ Boys' Life on the Battlefield ~ Part 2

description:
Japanese title: Ugokidasumono-tachi (動き出すものたち)

After hunting down the Four Tails, Itachi and Kisame are summoned by the leader of the Akatsuki.
name: Assemble

first_appearance_objects.name: Demonic Statue of the Outer Path

object_credits.name: Demonic Statue of the Outer Path

description:
Japanese title: Tansaku (探索)

Under Kakashi’s command, the Leaf ninja set off to find Itachi. Using Kakashi’s ninja hounds, they gather as much information as they can on Itachi. Meanwhile, the members of the Hebi also scatter to look for information on Itachi.
name: The Hunt

description:
Japanese title: Gekitotsu! (激突!)

Upon encountering one another, Sasuke and Deidara engage in battle. After exchanging a few blows to test Sasuke’s strength, Deidara conjures up his specialty clay dragon and wages long-range attacks against Sasuke from high above.
name: Clash!

first_appearance_objects.name: Demonic Statue of the Outer Path

object_credits.name: Demonic Statue of the Outer Path

description:
Japanese title: Geijutsu (芸術)

Determined to destroy the Sharingan to rid himself of the taste of defeat he received from Itachi, Deidara unleashes his biggest attack, the C4 Karura.
name: Art

description:
Japanese title: Shōshitsu (消失)

Sasuke goes missing after being caught by Deidara’s suicidal bombing. Sensing his disappearance, Jugo, Karin, and Suigetsu race to Sasuke’s last location, where the three Hebi members discover...?
name: Disappearance

description: Fish Mooney reveals a secret of Oswald Cobblepot's, prompting Maroni to take him on a trip to test his loyalty. Meanwhile, Gordon and Bullock hunt down a killer who targets victims with severe phobias and Bruce Wayne confronts Gordon for failing to make progress on his parents' murder case.
name: The Fearsome Dr. Crane

description: Gordon and Bullock set out to stop Gerald Crane, a biology teacher who has been harvesting the glands of his murder victims. Meanwhile, after finding herself in an unusual setting, Mooney continues plotting to gain power, and Falcone attempts to change Maroni's plan for the Penguin. Then, Bruce takes a treacherous hike.
name: The Scarecrow

description: When John (Matt Ryan) heads to a local hospital to investigate a mysterious attack, he enlists an unwitting Manny (Harold Perrineau) to help him. Meanwhile, a health scare causes Zed (Angelica Celaya) to question the source of her visions.
name: Angels and Ministers of Grace

has_staff_review.name: Constantine Episode #112 "Angels and Ministers of Grace"

description: The other Titans always drive Raven nuts, but it's much worse on Crazy Day.
name: Crazy Day

description: Beast Boy and Cyborg try to get the other Titans to eat without chewing.
name: Smile Bones

description: Tree Trunks and Mr. Pig's child, Sweet P, runs into trouble on his first day of school.
name: Gold Stars

description: A vision leads Finn to a friendly civilization and a mysterious crash site.
name: The Visitor

description: Lisa discovers that Springfield's anthem was lifted from another town, so she composes a new one, while Homer gets a big lesson in "Wide Pride."
name: Walking Big & Tall

description: When Marge gets fed up with the thankless duty of chauffeuring her kids around, she begins working as a driver for a transportation app service. Meanwhile, Homer bankrupts Moe when he watches over the bar for one night, which forces Moe to take a temporary job as a janitor at the nuclear plant.
name: My Fare Lady
